snippet.description:

If you‚Äôre serious about stomping roachies, then you‚Äôll want to pick up new weapons issues by O.X.R. ike the Leadspitter 3000 minigun, Sweeper Shotgun, O.X.R. Rifle, Wrecker Revolver, or the laser-guided Swarmstrike rocket launcher.

snippet.title: HIM | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
What would you sacrifice to become the greatest of all time?

From Oscar¬Æ winner Jordan Peele and Monkeypaw Productions, producers of the landmark horror films Get Out, Us, Candyman and Nope, comes a chilling journey into the inner sanctum of fame, idolatry and the pursuit of excellence at any cost, featuring an electrifying dramatic performance from Marlon Wayans (Air, Respect).

Former college wide-receiver Tyriq Withers (Atlanta, the upcoming I Know What You Did Last Summer) plays Cameron Cade, a rising-star quarterback who has devoted his life, and identity, to football. On the eve of professional football‚Äôs annual scouting Combine, Cam is attacked by an unhinged fan and suffers a potentially career-ending brain trauma.

Just when all seems lost, Cam receives a lifeline when his hero, Isaiah White (Marlon Wayans), a legendary eight-time Championship quarterback and cultural megastar, offers to train Cam at Isaiah‚Äôs isolated compound that he shares with his celebrity influencer wife, Elsie White (Julia Fox; Uncut Gems, No Sudden Move). But as Cam‚Äôs training accelerates, Isaiah‚Äôs charisma begins to curdle into something darker, sending his prot√©g√© down a disorienting rabbit hole that may cost him more than he ever bargained for.

The film features a dynamic supporting cast including alternative comedy legend Tim Heidecker (First Time Female Director, Us) and Australian comic Jim Jefferies (The Jim Jefferies Show), plus MMA heavyweight fighter Maurice Greene and hip hop phenoms Guapdad 4000 and Grammy nominee Tierra Whack, all three in their feature film debuts.

HIM is directed by Justin Tipping (Kicks) from an acclaimed Black List screenplay by Zack Akers & Skip Bronkie (creators of the sci-fi crime series Limetown) and by Justin Tipping. The film is produced by Ian Cooper (Nope, Us), Jordan Peele (Candyman, BlacKkKlansman), Win Rosenfeld (Candyman, Lovecraft Country) and Jamal M. Watson (Hala, Sprinter) for Monkeypaw Productions and is executive produced by David Kern and Monkeypaw‚Äôs Kate Oh.

https://www.himmovie.com/

snippet.description:
It‚Äôs time to show out and tell the world to Check My Game. Pre-order NHL 26 to play 7 Days Early now! https://x.ea.com/85081

Play like a superstar in EA SPORTS‚Ñ¢ NHL¬Æ 26. That starts with ICE-Q 2.0, now powered by NHL EDGE data, so your favorite superstars think, move, and play like their on-ice selves. Data-informed Attributes and Tendencies make star players perform in true-to-life fashion, with their playstyles and decision-making game-aware and impactful. A fine-tuned and enhanced arsenal of 28 X-Factors spans five different categories and is driven by unique animations, tactical gameplay outcomes, and tiers of impact, turning each into a formidable on-ice weapon. Superstars now truly feel like superstars.

The all-new Goalie Crease Control System brings an upgraded awareness between the posts with new close-range and reflex saves that allow for readjustments in reaction to puck deflections, poke checks, and improved AI positioning, giving goalies increased control over the blue paint. What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.description:
Discover the joy of unexpected connections. RENTAL FAMILY, starring Academy Award¬Æ winner Brendan Fraser. Premiering at @TIFF 2025, only in theaters November 21st. #RentalFamily

Set against modern-day Tokyo, RENTAL FAMILY follows an American actor (Brendan Fraser) who struggles to find purpose until he lands an unusual gig: working for a Japanese "rental family" agency, playing stand-in roles for strangers. As he immerses himself in his clients‚Äô worlds, he begins to form genuine bonds that blur the lines between performance and reality. Confronting the moral complexities of his work, he rediscovers purpose, belonging, and the quiet beauty of human connection.

Screenplay by: HIKARI, Stephen Blahut
Produced by: Eddie Vaisman, p.g.a, Julia Lebedev, p.g.a, HIKARI, p.g.a, Shin Yamaguchi, p.g.a

Explore brand-new Starry Stages that transform familiar locations, use all-new Mouthful Modes to reach new areas, and more. Kirby and the Forgotten Land ‚Äì Nintendo Switch 2 Edition + Star-Crossed World launches on Nintendo Switch 2 August 28, 2025.

snippet.title: Eden - Official Trailer (2025) Jude Law, Ana de Armas, Vanessa Kirby
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for Eden, an upcoming movie starring Jude Law, Ana de Armas, Vanessa Kirby, Daniel Br√ºhl, and Sydney Sweeney.

From Academy Award‚Äìwinning director Ron Howard, Eden unravels the shocking true story of a group of disillusioned outsiders (Jude Law, Ana de Armas, Vanessa Kirby, Daniel Br√ºhl, and Sydney Sweeney) who abandon modern society in search of a new beginning. Settling on a remote, uninhabited island, their utopian dream quickly unravels as they discover that the greatest threat isn‚Äôt the brutal climate or deadly wildlife, but each other. What follows is a chilling descent into chaos where tensions spiral, desperation takes hold, and a twisted power struggle leads to betrayal, violence, and the deaths of half the colony.

Eden is produced by Brian Grazer, Ron Howard, Karen Lunder, Stuart Ford, William M. Connor, and Patrick Newall. It is written by Noah Pink.

Eden, directed by Ron Howard, opens in theaters on August 22, 2025.

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 - Official Gameplay Overview - Amon
snippet.description:
‚ñ∫ Pre-order Borderlands 4 Now: https://2kgam.es/Borderlands4

Amon is the Forgeknight of Borderlands 4, a resilient and highly customizable frontliner who can use his weaponized drones to adapt to any situation.

His Forge arsenal lets him attack or defend as needed, ready to pulverize enemies with a Forgehammer, slice them in twain with Forgeaxes, soak up damage with a Forgeshield, and much, much more.

Read up on Amon's Skill Tree and Action Skills in full here: https://borderlands.2k.com/borderlands-4/game-info/vault-hunters/amon/

We‚Äôll be rolling out a Gameplay Overview, Character Short, and Vault Hunter page for all 4 Vault Hunters before launch ‚Äì so stay tuned!

Borderlands 4 is now available for pre-order on PlayStation¬Æ5, Xbox Series X|S, and Nintendo Switch 2, and pre-purchase on PC via Steam and the Epic Games Store! üí•

--------------------------------------------

Borderlands 4 is a mayhem-fueled looter shooter, jam-packed with billions of weapons, outrageous enemies, and intense co-op action. Explore a dangerous hidden planet Kairos as one of four new badass Vault Hunters.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. nl-NL.title: Ik stop niet totdat ik een handbetaling krijg!
nl-NL.description:
We zijn TERUG in het casino met een nieuwe vlog, en we zijn druk bezig met alle spellen. Ons ENIGE doel voor deze vlog is om een Hand-Pay te behalen, en we beschouwen de vlog als een succes. Heel erg bedankt allemaal voor het liken, abonneren en het achterlaten van jullie reacties. Zelfs als jullie me belachelijk maken, hou ik nog steeds van jullie. Jullie zijn allemaal prachtig, en ik waardeer het enorm dat jullie allemaal mee hebben gereisd op deze gekke reis. Wens me succes, en ik zie jullie bij de volgende! Laten we ten strijde trekken.

Brettski stormde als een bezetene door de glinsterende deuren van Hollywood Casino Bangor. Zijn ogen waren gericht op de jungle van gokautomaten ‚Äì draaiende lichtjes, klinkende munten, loze hoop. Hij was hier niet om te spelen. Hij was hier om te winnen. Een Hand-Pay ‚Äì de ongrijpbare jackpot waarbij de machine vastloopt, sirenes loeien en een zaalwachter verschijnt met een stapel geld alsof het een heilig geschrift is. Dit was geen spel. Het was het lot.

Hij liep langs de gokkasten met een paar centen ‚Äì te lage inzetten. Hij gleed langs de highroller-ruimte ‚Äì te voor de hand liggend. Zijn gevoel leidde hem naar een stoffige hoek waar een vergeten machine genaamd "Buffalo Inferno Gold Maxx" zachtjes zoemde. Hij gloeide. Een teken? Misschien. Hij stopte er een kraakhelder biljet van $100 in. Maximale inzet. Draaien.

Niets.

Draaien.

Niets.

Toen ‚Äì een flikkering. Gratis spellen.

Zijn hart bonsde. De rollen dansten ‚Äì wilds stapelden zich op, multipliers brulden en het scherm explodeerde in kleur. Jackpot.

Toen ‚Äì duisternis.

De lichten flikkerden. De machine liep vast. Maar geen geluid. Geen muziek voor handmatig uitbetalen. Geen medewerker. Op het scherm verscheen:
"FOUTCODE 44: HANDMATIGE VERIFICATIE VEREIST."

Hij hield iemand aan. De medewerker arriveerde met grote ogen. "Meneer... deze machine is al twee jaar niet meer actief geweest. Hij is uitgeschakeld. Er is geen jackpot aan gekoppeld in het systeem."

"Wat? Ik heb hem gewoon geraakt!" blafte Brettski.

De pitboss werd gebeld. Een beveiligingsteam volgde.

Ze haalden de bewakingsbeelden tevoorschijn... en snakten naar adem.

"Je hebt de machine niet aangeraakt," fluisterde de pitboss. "Hij draaide vanzelf."

Brettski's hart zonk in zijn schoenen. De camera toonde hem stilstaand, met zijn arm bevroren midden in zijn greep ‚Äì en de machine draaide vanzelf.

Er klonk een zacht pinggeluid.

Het scherm gaf nu aan:
"Welkom terug, Brettski. Klaar voor ronde twee?"

Wordt vervolgd.

Wie is Brettski? Brettski is een professionele gokker, vergelijkbaar met de oude legendes Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, Mr. Hand Pay of Lady Luck HQ! In tegenstelling tot deze legendes beschikt Brettski echter over duizenden jaren aan opgeslagen, oude kennis, verzameld door de ouderen, over vaardigheden zoals gokautomaten, roulette, blackjack, craps, bubble craps, poker en baccarat. Brettski's doel als professionele gokker is simpel: heel Las Vegas veroveren met geld dat hij verdient met gokken. Abonneer je om zijn reis naar wereldheerschappij te steunen.

snippet.title: America's Best Tank Goes Nuclear
snippet.description:
Many War Thunder players want Gaijin to add historical matchmaking, which would theoretically allow tanks like the 75mm M4 Shermans to meet with not only Tigers and Panthers, but King Tigers as well. I decided to see how well I could do in such a matchup. 

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.

Songs used (in order from first to last):
C&C: Generals Soundtrack
Ace Combat OST

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/spookston

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
